caption.title: Spatial structure of average phase lags of seasonal dengue in Brazilian regions.
caption.p: (A) state level, (B,C) meso- and micro-regions, (D,E,F) urban subdivisions. Administrative boundaries for Brazilian municipalities were obtained from IBGE ( https://www.ibge.gov.br/geociencias-novoportal/cartas-e-mapas.html), along with shapefiles for Urban-Regional divisions ( https://ww2.ibge.gov.br/home/geociencias/geografia/default_divisao_urbano_regional.shtm).
